{"tid":111720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(小心食唔落飯)用屎做臭豆腐 踢爆10大中國黑心食物","createTime":"2017-02-07T15:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T22:10:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86b597d859b9e52bb5fbf9ea8c6762cac825a1c5","tid":111720,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"早前本港爆出「假米」疑雲，雖然政府化驗證明「真的假不了」，全部懷疑「假米」均為真米，而香港市民如此緊張無可厚非，因近年中國黑心食物醜聞層出不窮，實在令人防不勝防。<br />\n<br />\n回顧近年中國發現的十大黑心食物（見下表），對中國有機食物可以賣貴幾倍，也多一份理解。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.financeapp.edigest.com.hk/supload/articlecelebrity_920x483_0/8146/589834104e8b3_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.financeapp.edigest.com.hk%2Fsupload%2Farticlecelebrity_920x483_0%2F8146%2F589834104e8b3_1.jpg&h=0ff655fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edigest.hk/Vip/detail?id=8146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2FVip%2Fdetail%3Fid%3D8146&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0175b4d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.edigest.hk/Vip/detail?id=8146</a>"},{"pid":"5db2ca639111107f8c1c4a03c66f812e99085e81","tid":111720,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cd1667b42ce004c13c99f7a3b84b92403b65a4","tid":111720,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爆炸西瓜<br />\n孔雀石綠"},{"pid":"1fdf771e54f5dd4d25ede14c7bfc338477488ebf","tid":111720,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,